{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"primary-lipophobic-dugong","description":"## Context\nStore `{provider, external_id}` keyed on the provider's opaque id (never email) and resolve outbound Jira assignee/reporter by accountId behind a provider seam, with graceful degradation.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Mappings key on the provider's opaque id; a provider-seam interface exposes resolve(provider, external_id)->identity.\n- [ ] Reconciler sets the Jira assignee by accountId, bootstraps via `/user/search` best-effort, degrades to project-default(-1)/unassigned without hard-failing when email is hidden (test with fixture identity + stubbed accountId).\n- [ ] Reporter set by accountId where Modify-Reporter is granted; documented degradation otherwise.","id":"264f-673a-e821-4a82","parent_id":"e68d-b701-4dd9-47aa","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"identity: provider-neutral mapping + Jira adapter (outbound assignee/reporter)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783735873790354001,"uuid":"389f64e2-b23c-4633-8106-e335b3494f32"}